simplesect.title: Xlib Compose Keys for pt_BR.UTF-8
simplesect.para: Applications using Xlib input handling should recognize these compose key sequences in locales using the pt_BR.UTF-8 compose table.
UTF-8 (Unicode) compose sequence David.Monniaux@ens.fr Modified for Brazilian Portuguese by Gustavo Noronha Silva <kov@debian.org>
